snippet.title: Pi and Buffon's Matches - Numberphile
snippet.description:
Our Pi Playlist (more videos): http://bit.ly/PiPlaylist
Dr Tony Padilla's unique (and low budget) twist on the Buffon's Needle experiment to learn the true value of Pi.
More links & stuff in full description below ↓↓↓
